    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The up/down arrow keys for history search are handled by readline - I suspect IPython's settings are revealing a bug in there. You can override IPython's defaults for readline by setting other actions for those keys in `~/.inputrc`, or in IPython config by setting `InteractiveShell.readline_parse_and_bind`.\n"
